There are two ways to align a molecule:

1. the python script align_pqr.py
  - finds center of mass
  - shifts to (0,0,0)
  - finds least-squares line through data
  - orients z-axis to this line

  ----> 1BNA_align.pqr

2. use http://www.ks.uiuc.edu/Research/vmd/script_library/scripts/orient/

  ----> 1BNA_orient.pqr
